<p>Because I can exercise and share!</p>
<section id="my-word" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="my-word">My word</h2>
<p>I canâ€™t help but feel a sense of pride and great accomplishment as the year comes to an end. In 2023, I committed to fitness goals which involved gym weight-lifting and outdoor running exercises, targeting at least 11km each weekend (spoiler: I only did 22km, ~ approximately 2 weekends), nevertheless, the results is a whooping 100 days of hard-work, dedication and near addiction to gym work-out.</p>
<p>In this short article, I will share my 100 days journey, motivations and the lessons I have picked up in the process.</p>
